    <p>In order to understand the wine ecosystem, I talked with consumers, producers, distributors, and retail wine shops, writing and refining interview guides for each role I interviewed.</p>
    <p>After two weeks of interviews, I collated all my notes into a master document and extracted the key insights to clarify my understanding of the wine industry and its problems.</p>
